Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただの夢　(sweet dream)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:10.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なのに胸　(ずっと)
